# Design System

Before generating or modifying any visual component, read `DESIGN.md` at the project root.

Rules:
- Use ONLY the colors defined in DESIGN.md
- Follow the typographic scale exactly
- Apply spacing values from the Layout Principles section
- Follow component patterns from the Component Stylings section
- Never violate the Do's and Don'ts section
- When in doubt, reference DESIGN.md — do not invent new values
